OL,4,CMiscarriages and stillbirths: New
OL,5,CZealand to allow bereavement leave
OL,6, Couples in New Zealand who have a
OL,7, miscarriage or stillbirth will be
OL,8, eligible for paid bereavement leave
OL,9, under a new law approved by parliament.
OL,11,FMP Ginny Andersen, who put forward the
OL,12,Fbill, said it would allow mothers and
OL,13,Ftheir partners to "come to terms with
OL,14,Ftheir loss" without taking sick leave.
OL,16,FThe bill also applies to those having a
OL,17,Fchild though adoption or surrogacy.
OL,19,FNew Zealand is reportedly only the
OL,20,Fsecond country in the world to
OL,21,Fintroduce the measure, after India.
